◆ GetBaseClassPointerToNodes()

virtual CVariable* CSolver::GetBaseClassPointerToNodes ( )
protectedpure virtual

Pure virtual function, all derived solvers MUST implement a method returning their "nodes".

Note
Don't forget to call SetBaseClassPointerToNodes() in the constructor of the derived CSolver.
Returns
Nodes of the solver, upcast to their base class (CVariable).
